      "date": "2015-06-30 04:52:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/5922884a-1ee3-11e5-a01b-5254006e85c2).  Ran 6 tests.  No failures.",
